    <entry>
      <title>Manjaro安装后的初始配置</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/23/ManjaroSetting/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/23/ManjaroSetting/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>​        <a href="https://manjaro.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Manjaro</a>是基于<a href="https://www.archlinux.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Arch Linux</a>的发行版，因此有着Arch所具有的优秀包管理器，并且没有Arch所带来的滚动式更新所带来的不稳定。</p><p>​        最为突出的就是有着非常强大的<a href="https://aur.archlinux.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AUR</a>源，这是个全球用户开发者所共同维护的软件源，为Manjaro的使用不会为软件的匮乏而担心。</p><p>​    由于Manjaro的默认源都是在国外，若是不对其进行相应的配置，作为国内使用者则会使用困难。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="1、设置国内源"><a href="#1、设置国内源" class="headerlink" title="1、设置国内源"></a>1、设置国内源</h2><p><code>Ctrl+Alt+T</code>打开终端</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syy</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S vim</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改配置文件，连接国内archlinuxcn源</p><p><code>sudo vim /etc/pacman.conf</code>在文档末尾添加</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Optional TrustedOnly</span><br><span class="line">Server = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/<span class="variable">$arch</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>Esc</code> + <code>:wq</code> 退出保存</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syy &amp;&amp; sudo pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、安装常用软件"><a href="#2、安装常用软件" class="headerlink" title="2、安装常用软件"></a>2、安装常用软件</h2><h3 id="（1）git"><a href="#（1）git" class="headerlink" title="（1）git"></a>（1）git</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（2）yay"><a href="#（2）yay" class="headerlink" title="（2）yay"></a>（2）yay</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（3）chromium"><a href="#（3）chromium" class="headerlink" title="（3）chromium"></a>（3）chromium</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S chromium</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（4）Typora"><a href="#（4）Typora" class="headerlink" title="（4）Typora"></a>（4）Typora</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（5）wps-office"><a href="#（5）wps-office" class="headerlink" title="（5）wps office"></a>（5）wps office</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S wps-office ttf-wps-fonts wps-office-mui-zh-cn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（6）Sublime-Text3"><a href="#（6）Sublime-Text3" class="headerlink" title="（6）Sublime Text3"></a>（6）Sublime Text3</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -O https://download.sublimetext.com/sublimehq-pub.gpg &amp;&amp; sudo pacman-key --add sublimehq-pub.gpg &amp;&amp; sudo pacman-key --lsign-key 8A8F901A &amp;&amp; rm sublimehq-pub.gpg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Stable Edition</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="string">"\n[sublime-text]\nServer = https://download.sublimetext.com/arch/stable/x86_64"</span> | sudo tee -a /etc/pacman.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Dev Edition</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="string">"\n[sublime-text]\nServer = https://download.sublimetext.com/arch/dev/x86_64"</span> | sudo tee -a /etc/pacman.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syu sublime-text</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（7）网易云音乐"><a href="#（7）网易云音乐" class="headerlink" title="（7）网易云音乐"></a>（7）网易云音乐</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S netease-cloud-music</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（8）中文输入法"><a href="#（8）中文输入法" class="headerlink" title="（8）中文输入法"></a>（8）中文输入法</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S fcitx-im fcitx-configtool fcitx-sogoupinyin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（9）Pycharm编辑器"><a href="#（9）Pycharm编辑器" class="headerlink" title="（9）Pycharm编辑器"></a>（9）Pycharm编辑器</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#专业版</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S pycharm</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#社区版</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S pycharm-community-edition</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、安装软件后配置修改"><a href="#3、安装软件后配置修改" class="headerlink" title="3、安装软件后配置修改"></a>3、安装软件后配置修改</h2><h3 id="（1）中文输入法无法调用"><a href="#（1）中文输入法无法调用" class="headerlink" title="（1）中文输入法无法调用"></a>（1）中文输入法无法调用</h3><p><code>Ctrl+Alt+T</code>打开终端，<code>cd ~ &amp;&amp; vim .xprofile</code>，添加</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> XMODIFIERS=<span class="string">"@im=fcitx"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改保存后，<code>reboot</code>重启</p><h3 id="（2）wps-office无法输入中文"><a href="#（2）wps-office无法输入中文" class="headerlink" title="（2）wps office无法输入中文"></a>（2）wps office无法输入中文</h3><p>修改/usr/bin下以下执行文件</p><p><code>sudo vim /usr/bin/wps</code>,<code>sudo vim /usr/bin/et</code></p><p><code>sudo vim /usr/bin/wpp</code>,<code>sudo vim /usr/bin/wpspdf</code></p><p>在第一行<code>#!/bin/bash</code>下加入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> XMODIFIERS=<span class="string">"@im=fcitx"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（3）网易云音乐无法输入中文"><a href="#（3）网易云音乐无法输入中文" class="headerlink" title="（3）网易云音乐无法输入中文"></a>（3）网易云音乐无法输入中文</h3><p>安装qecf库</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://gitee.com/JerryHM11/qcef_build.git ~</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -U qcef-1.1.6-1-x86_64.pkg.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>vim /opt/netease/netease-cloud-music/netease-cloud-music.bash</code>  修改为</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">!/bin/sh</span></span><br><span class="line">HERE="$(dirname "$(readlink -f "$&#123;0&#125;")")"</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">export</span> LD_LIBRARY_PATH=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;HERE&#125;</span>"</span>/libs</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">export</span> QT_PLUGIN_PATH=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;HERE&#125;</span>"</span>/plugins </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="built_in">export</span> QT_QPA_PLATFORM_PLUGIN_PATH=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$&#123;HERE&#125;</span>"</span>/plugins/platforms</span></span><br><span class="line">export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib</span><br><span class="line">export XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=DDE</span><br><span class="line">exec "$&#123;HERE&#125;"/netease-cloud-music $@</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​                    </p><h2 id="4、使用oh-my-zsh美化终端"><a href="#4、使用oh-my-zsh美化终端" class="headerlink" title="4、使用oh-my-zsh美化终端"></a>4、使用oh-my-zsh美化终端</h2><h3 id="（1）安装oh-my-zsh-manjaro自带zsh（zsh-≠-oh-my-zsh）"><a href="#（1）安装oh-my-zsh-manjaro自带zsh（zsh-≠-oh-my-zsh）" class="headerlink" title="（1）安装oh-my-zsh    #manjaro自带zsh（zsh ≠ oh-my-zsh）"></a>（1）安装oh-my-zsh    #manjaro自带zsh（zsh ≠ oh-my-zsh）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#curl方式</span></span><br><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#wget方式</span></span><br><span class="line">sh -c <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$(wget https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)</span>"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（2）插件安装-推荐两个常用的，其余的插件可以上GitHub上了解"><a href="#（2）插件安装-推荐两个常用的，其余的插件可以上GitHub上了解" class="headerlink" title="（2）插件安装    #推荐两个常用的，其余的插件可以上GitHub上了解"></a>（2）插件安装    #推荐两个常用的，其余的插件可以上GitHub上了解</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#自动补全插件</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions <span class="variable">$ZSH_CUSTOM</span>/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#语法高亮插件</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git <span class="variable">$ZSH_CUSTOM</span>/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（3）安装后启用插件"><a href="#（3）安装后启用插件" class="headerlink" title="（3）安装后启用插件"></a>（3）安装后启用插件</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>& bash</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.zshrc    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 在plugins后括号里添加安装的插件名字</span></span><br><span class="line">plugins=( git </span><br><span class="line">          zsh-autosuggestions </span><br><span class="line">          zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> 最后刷新，使配置生效</span></span><br><span class="line">source ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
